# ==================================================
# Prerequisites – Start Services
# ==================================================
#
# Start receiver:
#   Open a terminal and run:
#     npm run dev:receiver
#   The receiver will listen on:
#     http://localhost:3000
#
# Start sender:
#   Open another terminal and run:
#     npm run dev:sender
#   The sender will listen on:
#     http://localhost:3001
#
# ==================================================


### Create Subscription
POST http://localhost:3001/subscriptions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "callbackUrl": "http://localhost:3000/webhook",
  "events": ["item.created"],
  "secret": "your-shared-secret-key"
}

###

### Trigger Event
POST http://localhost:3001/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event": "item.created",
  "data": {
    "itemId": "abc-123"
  }
}

# ==================================================
# Expected Result
# ==================================================
#
# - Sender responds with a payload delivery result
# - Receiver receives the webhook at:
#     http://localhost:3000/webhook
# - Receiver logs the request
# - Receiver responds with:
#
#   { "status": "received" }
#
# ==================================================